<div metal:use-macro="view.global_template">
    <div metal:fill-slot="content">
        <h1>${page_title}</h1>
        <p>This <em>STORM Dashboard</em> makes STORM leadership,
            coaches, and team managers more productive by focusing
            on the primary tasks to make an effective travel club:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>See rosters (coaches, managers, goalies,
                players) for each team</li>
            <li>Player and parent contact information</li>
            <li>For each team, who has/hasn't registered/paid for
                which tournaments</li>
            <li>Easily send an email to each team, or copy the list
                of email addresses</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
